We use a BLS train from Bern to Luzern.
In Wolhusen it changes the train number to 4487 (was 4387 before)
In a second modeling we want to model the change in the train number as also shown in the example.
In this version the train goes to Luzern exactly as shown in the image.

VM Nr. 4357
Bern                    20:36
Konolfingen       20:52 20:52
Langnau i.E       21:05 21:06
